reviewText: I facilitate an anger managment class and this is only a 25 minute video.  It's not very educational, it has a highlight of Lewis Black and some experts talking about why venting anger doesn't work among some other segments.
Ok resource not great for group work in a professional setting
Bought this item for a group I do with men who are abusive toward women. Showed it in group. Men thought it was helpful and appropriate for the group.
